description:
&lt;p&gt;We have a vacancy for a full time ‘Senior Payroll Officer’ in our busy payroll services department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant must have a minimum of 4 years NHS (ESR) Payroll experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is specifically for a trained NHS Payroll officer to progress into, as it requires detailed knowledge and experience of NHS ESR Payroll to provide support for more junior staff and cover and support to the payroll team manager.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further information or details of this role, please contact Darren Gatward Head of Payroll Services on 0118 3226666.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
